{"tid":975624,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"中學有無遇過啲好有教學熱誠嘅老師","createTime":"2019-01-09T20:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T08:30:30.000Z","uid":47374,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9dfdf407a8a1ea950ba5e74986457ad64592524b","tid":975624,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T20:02:28.000Z","msg":"十幾年前ce Maths，<br />\n個老師將多年嚟嘅pastpaper分晒課題比我地操，<br />\n再定期私人醒多一堆自製練習比我地放假做，<br />\n而嗰期佢自己夜晚都要讀書考試，<br />\n咁啲練習最後當然有人無做或者鳩做，<br />\n之後佢上堂屌我地屌到自己眼濕濕，<br />\n感動到好多人補做返堆練習，<br />\n雖然我對Maths無性趣，但諗返真係幸慶比佢教過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後AL教M＆s嗰個呀Sir hea到仆街，好大反差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c4d135372986e9ad5e8e5ad55c30d2956baa1c","tid":975624,"uid":196719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T23:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ea1b5ef6bd1e3cb74f04fc93b3036a8a0e52cb","tid":975624,"uid":215915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T08:30:30.000Z","msg":"第一堂一入黎就話跟佢嘅方法通識五星星無難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地上堂上到頹上到攰就盡佢一切能力谷翻精神我地<br />\n但唔知係咪我地實在太頹同埋學校啲行政野搞到佢個團火越黎越細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都好多謝佢比我上到人生中幾正幾好玩嘅通識堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}